Most Important Advice ⚠️
Do NOT try to fully plan 200 stories immediately.
Do this instead:
1.	Define all epics
2.	Fully detail ONLY next 1–2 epics
3.	Build
4.	Learn
5.	Refactor roadmap
This mirrors real engineering teams.
Because once you actually build:
•	architecture changes
•	priorities change
•	pain points appear
•	better ideas emerge
That evolution is part of becoming strong.

🔵 EPIC 1 — Core Backend Foundation
🎯 Epic Goal
Build a clean, production-style backend foundation for InstaClone.
This epic focuses on:
•	backend architecture
•	API design
•	validation
•	exception handling
•	clean code structure
•	scalability preparation
By the end of this epic, the project should feel like a real backend system instead of a tutorial app.
